{"tid":1934051,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"週經系列：咩叫愛一個人","createTime":"2020-03-19T16:21:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T04:58:46.000Z","uid":305822,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"75cd7311c34fcc3c0966eacfe1aab12bd659a5a3","tid":1934051,"uid":305822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T16:21:01.000Z","msg":"成日覺得呢個問題好有趣，可以反映一個人嘅愛情觀，同埋過往經歷都會影響到答案。<br />\n<br />\n我先，以前覺得愛一個人係佔有或者轟轟烈烈驚天動地。<br />\n經歷多左，而家覺得愛一個人會願意為佢付出，會企喺佢角度諗嘢（分分鐘仲多過幫自己諗），將自己變好（例如事業上學業上，改曬d脾氣，唔自私，唔周圍吊住其他異性）<br />\n同埋最重要嘅係見到佢開心我就夠了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b7ffba86ae9ab09fb799b4227a4d2649afe6861","tid":1934051,"uid":251510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T16:22:15.000Z","msg":"是<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd5c884b272f829f2a32686eb31da04c5406efb9","tid":1934051,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T16:23:15.000Z","msg":"是<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e0866f880432048a43314c95365c089122224d6","tid":1934051,"uid":91767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75cd7311c34fcc3c0966eacfe1aab12bd659a5a3","tid":1934051,"uid":305822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T16:21:01.000Z","msg":"成日覺得呢個問題好有趣，可以反映一個人嘅愛情觀，同埋過往經歷都會影響到答案。<br />\n<br />\n我先，以前覺得愛一個人係佔有或者轟轟烈烈驚天動地。<br />\n經歷多左，而家覺得愛一個人會願意為佢付出，會企喺佢角度諗嘢（分分鐘仲多過幫自己諗），將自己變好（例如事業上學業上，改曬d脾氣，唔自私，唔周圍吊住其他異性）<br />\n同埋最重要嘅係見到佢開心我就夠了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T16:23:19.000Z","msg":"岩，就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b903bede7bff4860fa0faeaa297f37c176f230","tid":1934051,"uid":192075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T16:24:22.000Z","msg":"我自己好純綷<br />\n我自己唔